  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The proposed single storey rear extension, due to the excessive size and scale and inappropriate position and design, would harm neighbours living conditions, in terms of loss of light, outlook and increased sense of enclosure, contrary to adopted Local Plan policies CC2 (Urban Design and Architecture) and SC7 (Residential Extensions and Alterations) and the Residential Extension Guidelines.",
    "Reason : 2 - The proposed single storey rear extension and front porch, by reason of their excessive scale and inappropriate design, would be overbearing and visually obtrusive features failing to remain subordinate to the main house harming its character and that of the surrounding area, contrary to adopted Local Plan policies CC1 (Context and Character), CC2 (Urban Design and Architecture) and SC7 (Residential Extensions and Alterations) and the Residential Extension Guidelines."
